
TY  - JOUR
T1  - Architecture of Power Markets
AU  - Wilson, Robert
Y1  - 2002/07/01
PY  - 2002
DA  - 2002/07/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/1468-0262.00334
T2  - Econometrica
